data.description: Wolfork Valley & Mountain Views..... Come and see this large 3 bedroom 3.5 bath home on 4.23 acres. Every room is LARGE!!! Lots of space to you to enjoy. Main bedroom is on the main level and is privately located. Spacious living and dining room is great for family or friend gatherings  Nicely situated on the lot, you can capture wonderful views from the screened porch. The yard has hundreds of hostas. Lots of room for those with a green thumb or the love of gardening.
